.begxmpl g/(abc)*/ execute Iabc\e
For every line that matches the regular expression
.param (abc)*
.ct , execute the keystrokes
.param Iabc&lt.ESC&gt.
(this will insert the characters abc at the start of the line).
.endxmpl
.xmplsect end
