.keyref map
command, only all characters in &parm2 work as their base meaning; that is,
all key mappings are ignored and the keys have their default
behaviour.
.enddescr
.alsosee begin
.seethis execute
.seethis keyadd
.seethis map
.seethis unmap
.alsosee end
.endfunc

