If a variable is a boolean variable, then it is be set via
.millust begin
set var    - set var to TRUE
set novar  - set var to FALSE
.millust end
.np
Variables other than boolean variables are set via
.millust begin
set var = test  - set var to 'test'
set var  test   - set var to 'test'
